1
00:00:01,360 --> 00:00:03,040
(DOCTOR WHO THEME)

2
00:00:09,520 --> 00:00:11,520
(TELEPHONE RINGING)

3
00:00:18,680 --> 00:00:20,800
DOCTOR ON ANSWERING MACHINE:
Oh, blimey! Okay.

4
00:00:20,880 --> 00:00:22,880
You can probably leave a message
at the tone or something.

5
00:00:22,960 --> 00:00:25,960
Sorry, I wasn't really trying to
do this, I was looking for the brakes!

6
00:00:26,160 --> 00:00:27,440
(ANSWERPHONE BEEPS)

7
00:00:28,000 --> 00:00:30,440
AMY: Doctor?
Doctor, can you hear me?

8
00:00:31,280 --> 00:00:33,000
Are you ever going to hear this?

9
00:00:33,080 --> 00:00:36,160
You don't even know you've
got an answerphone.

10
00:00:36,320 --> 00:00:40,440
How can you be so clever and so
completely stupid at the same time?

11
00:00:41,280 --> 00:00:43,560
Or if you can hear this,
please just pick up the phone.

12
00:00:43,960 --> 00:00:45,720
Don't get confused, I'm not invisible

13
00:00:45,800 --> 00:00:47,240
or trapped in a space bottle
or something.

14
00:00:47,320 --> 00:00:49,920
I'm just talking on the answerphone.

15
00:00:50,160 --> 00:00:52,200
Just pick up the phone!

16
00:00:53,800 --> 00:00:56,080
You said you'd find my baby.

17
00:00:56,240 --> 00:00:58,480
You said you'd find Melody.

18
00:00:58,640 --> 00:01:02,080
Have you found her?
Because you promised.

19
00:01:02,720 --> 00:01:06,160
I know she's going to be okay.
I know she'll grow up to be River,

20
00:01:06,480 --> 00:01:08,480
but that's not the point.

21
00:01:10,000 --> 00:01:12,600
I don't want to miss all those years,
you know, I..

22
00:01:14,080 --> 00:01:15,920
I can't stand it. Can't!

23
00:01:16,960 --> 00:01:18,960
Please, Doctor, please.

24
00:01:21,000 --> 00:01:24,520
Okay, phone me back
when you know something.

25
00:01:25,200 --> 00:01:27,760
Please, Doctor, at least do that.

26
00:01:28,000 --> 00:01:30,080
As soon as you know. Okay?

27
00:01:30,320 --> 00:01:31,880
All right, bye.

28
00:01:32,080 --> 00:01:34,200
(HANGS UP, ANSWERPHONE BEEPS)

29
00:01:34,360 --> 00:01:35,480
(SIGHS)

